  <lyrics>[V1]
 Acapach thaquinacajj
 Cawcsarus saraquiwa,
 Jaken amtataparjam
 Utt'ayataquiraquiw.
 
[C]
 Tatit Cristoquiw cheka thaquejja,
 Jupar arcapjjafiáni,
 Wifiay jacañ kori marcaruwa,
 Jupajj irpasjjestani. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Diosajj jaketaquejja,
 Pá thaqui uchawayi,
 Má thaquejja c'ullc'uwa,
 Má thaquisti anchowa.
 
[V3]
 Ancho thaquíquis ucajj,
 Infiernoruw irpasqui;
 ücampis c'ullc'u thaquejj,
 Alajjpacharuw irpi.
 
</lyrics></song>